INSERT INTO `visa` VALUES (1,1,'Admission letter from an Afghan institution.','Application Assistance, Document Verification','~$50','1. Secure admission.\n2. Apply at the nearest Afghan embassy with required documents.','Incomplete application forms.','Kabuli Pulao, Mantu.','For students enrolled in recognized Afghan schools or universities.','* Passport\n* Admission Letter\n* Financial Proof','Proof of funds to cover tuition and living expenses.','N/A','4-6 weeks','1 year','Education','1 year'),(1,2,'Highly restricted, case-by-case basis.','Legal Consultation, Special Permit Application','Varies','Requires special permits and government approvals, a very lengthy process.','Lack of proper sponsorship.','N/A','Long-term residency is extremely difficult to obtain for foreign nationals.','* Extensive personal and professional documentation.','Significant financial resources may be required.','N/A','Months','Long-term','Immigration','Varies'),(1,3,'Invitation letter or tour group required. Travel is highly discouraged.','Invitation Support, Tour Booking','~$100','1. Obtain an invitation or book a tour.\n2. Apply at an Afghan embassy.','Lack of a valid invitation or sponsor.','Bolani, Ashak.','Tourist visas are for sightseeing and visiting family.','* Passport\n* Invitation Letter\n* Proof of accommodation','Sufficient funds for the duration of stay.','Visit the Gardens of Babur in Kabul, see the Minaret of Jam.','2-4 weeks','30 days','Travel','3 months'),(1,4,'Invitation from a registered Afghan company.','Business Invitation Vetting, Legal Advisory','~$150','1. Secure an invitation from an Afghan business partner.\n2. Apply at the embassy.','Invitation from a non-reputable company.','N/A','For individuals visiting for business meetings, negotiations, or trade.','* Passport\n* Official Invitation Letter\n* Company Registration Documents','Letter from the sponsoring company confirming financial responsibility.','N/A','2-4 weeks','30 days','Business','3 months'),(2,5,'Enrollment in an Armenian educational institution.','Application Support, Post-Arrival Registration','~$10','1. Get accepted into a school.\n2. Apply for a student residency permit upon arrival.','Not applying for the residency permit in time after arrival.','Khorovats (BBQ), Dolma.','For students attending universities or other educational programs in Armenia.','* Passport\n* Enrollment Letter\n* Proof of accommodation','Sufficient funds for living expenses.','Explore Yerevan, visit the Geghard Monastery.','1-2 weeks','1 year','Education','1 year'),(2,6,'Based on work, investment, or Armenian heritage.','Residency Permit Help, Investment Advisory','Varies','1. Determine eligibility (work, family, etc.).\n2. Gather documents.\n3. Apply at the Passport and Visa Department in Yerevan.','Incomplete documentation.','N/A','Armenia offers temporary and permanent residency permits for various purposes.','* Passport\n* Application Form\n* Proof of Funds/Employment','Proof of stable income or sufficient savings.','N/A','2-3 months','Long-term','Immigration','1-5 years'),(2,7,'Visa-free for many nationalities.','Itinerary Planning, Local Tour Booking','Free','Simply arrive at the border with a valid passport if from a visa-exempt country.','Overstaying the visa-free period.','Harissa, Lavash bread.','For tourism and visiting friends or relatives.','* Valid Passport','N/A for visa-free entry.','Visit Tatev Monastery, hike in Dilijan National Park.','Visa-Free','Up to 180 days','Travel','180 days'),(2,8,'For establishing a business or investment.','Company Registration Help, Legal Consultation','~$70','1. Register a company or have an invitation.\n2. Apply for a business visa or residency permit.','Unclear business purpose.','N/A','For foreign nationals intending to conduct business activities in Armenia.','* Passport\n* Business Plan or Invitation Letter','Proof of investment or business registration.','N/A','1-2 weeks','Up to 1 year','Business','1 year'),(3,9,'Requires admission to an accredited institution.','University Application Support, Residency Permit Help','~$20','1. Secure admission.\n2. Apply for a single-entry visa.\n3. Apply for a temporary residence permit upon arrival.','Not registering with the State Migration Service.','N/A','For long-term study at Azerbaijani universities.','* Passport\n* Admission Letter\n* Completed Application','Proof of tuition payment and sufficient funds.','N/A','3-5 days','1 year','Education','1 year'),(3,10,'Work or investment-based residency permits.','Residency Application Guidance, Investment Advisory','Varies','1. Obtain a work permit or make an investment.\n2. Apply for a temporary residence permit.','Issues with work permit validation.','N/A','Residency is typically tied to employment or significant investment in the country.','* Passport\n* Work Contract or Investment Proof','A valid work permit or proof of investment of at least 500,000 AZN.','N/A','3-6 months','Long-term','Immigration','Varies'),(3,11,'ASAN e-Visa available for many nationalities.','E-Visa Application Service, Tour Planning','~$20','Apply online via the ASAN Visa portal.','Applying through unofficial websites.','Plov, Dolma, Kebab.','The ASAN Visa is a convenient e-visa for tourists from eligible countries.','* Passport Copy (digital)','N/A','Explore Baku\'s old city, see the mud volcanoes.','3 days','30 days','Travel','90 days'),(3,12,'E-Visa suitable for short business trips.','Business E-Visa Support, Itinerary Planning','~$20','Apply online via the ASAN Visa portal, selecting \'business\' as the purpose.','Overstaying the 30-day limit.','N/A','The ASAN e-Visa can also be used for short-term business meetings.','* Passport Copy (digital)','N/A','N/A','3 days','30 days','Business','90 days'),(4,13,'Sponsored by the educational institution in Bahrain.','Sponsorship Coordination, Application Filing','Varies','1. Gain admission.\n2. The institution handles the visa sponsorship application.','Delays caused by the sponsoring institution.','N/A','A student visa must be sponsored by the school or university.','* Passport\n* Sponsor Letter from school\n* Medical Certificate','Sponsorship from the institution is the primary requirement.','N/A','2-4 weeks','1 year','Education','1 year'),(4,14,'Typically requires employment sponsorship.','Work Permit Assistance, Job Search Support','Varies','1. Secure a job offer.\n2. Employer applies for your work permit and entry visa.','Employer failing to complete the sponsorship process correctly.','N/A','Residency is almost always tied to having a local employer sponsor your work permit.','* Passport\n* Employment Contract\n* Medical Certificate','A valid employment contract with a Bahraini company.','N/A','1-2 months','Long-term','Immigration','Varies'),(4,15,'E-Visa available for tourism purposes.','E-Visa Application, Tour Booking','~$25','Apply online through the official Bahrain e-Visa website.','Not having a hotel booking confirmation.','Machboos, Quzi.','An electronic visa is available for tourists from many countries.','* Passport\n* Onward Ticket\n* Hotel Booking','Proof of sufficient funds for your stay.','Visit the Bahrain National Museum, see the Tree of Life.','3-5 days','14 days','Travel','30 days'),(4,16,'Requires a local sponsor or company invitation.','Sponsor Arrangement, Corporate Services','~$80','Apply for an e-Visa with a letter from a local sponsoring company.','The sponsor letter not being correctly formatted.','N/A','For attending meetings, conferences, and trade fairs.','* Passport\n* Sponsor Letter\n* CR copy of the sponsoring company','A valid and registered Bahraini sponsor.','N/A','1 week','30 days','Business','1 year (multi-entry)'),(5,17,'Admission to a recognized Bangladeshi institution.','Student Visa Application, Document Checklist','~$50','Apply at a Bangladeshi embassy with the required documents.','Incomplete application form.','N/A','For students enrolled in full-time courses.','* Passport\n* Admission Letter\n* Bank Statement','Proof of financial solvency.','N/A','1-2 weeks','1 year','Education','1 year'),(5,18,'Primarily for investors and high-skilled workers.','Investment Visa Guidance, BIDA Liaison','Varies','Requires a recommendation from the Bangladesh Investment Development Authority (BIDA).','Bureaucratic delays.','N/A','Long-term residency options are available for significant investors.','* Passport\n* Investment Plan\n* BIDA Recommendation','Minimum investment thresholds must be met.','N/A','Months','Long-term','Immigration','Varies'),(5,19,'Visa on Arrival available for many nationalities for tourism.','VOA Checklist Prep, Tour Planning','~$20','Proceed to the Visa on Arrival counter upon landing.','Not having required documents in hand upon arrival.','Biryani, Hilsa fish curry.','For tourism, available at major international airports.','* Passport\n* Return Ticket\n* Proof of Funds','Sufficient funds (e.g., $500).','Explore the Sundarbans mangrove forest, visit tea gardens in Srimangal.','On Arrival','30 days','Travel','30 days'),(5,20,'Invitation from a Bangladeshi business entity.','Business Invitation Support, Application Filing','~$100','Apply at a Bangladeshi embassy with an invitation letter.','Lack of a proper invitation.','N/A','For business meetings, trade, and investment.','* Passport\n* Invitation Letter\n* Letter from your own company','A clear invitation from a registered Bangladeshi company.','N/A','1 week','30-90 days','Business','6-12 months'),(6,21,'Extremely rare; requires government approval.','Special Permit Consultation','Varies','Requires special permits and is handled on a case-by-case basis.','N/A','N/A','Long-term study is not a common pathway for foreigners.','* Case-by-case basis','Varies','N/A','Varies','Course Duration','Education','Varies'),(6,22,'Immigration to Bhutan is not generally possible.','Consultation','N/A','N/A','N/A','N/A','Bhutan does not have a standard immigration program for foreign nationals.','* N/A','N/A','N/A','N